@inherits AdminComponentBase

<Overview3Cols>
    <Text1>
        <strong>Metric Exporter</strong> is a tool that exports key Proxmox VE metrics to Prometheus.<br />
        It provides real-time insights into cluster performance, resource utilization, and system health.<br />
        By integrating with Prometheus, administrators can efficiently monitor and analyze Proxmox VE environments.<br />
    </Text1>

    <Text2>
        <strong>Enhanced Observability</strong>: Enables in-depth monitoring of VM, container, and node performance.<br />
        <strong>Proactive Alerting</strong>: Works with Prometheus Alertmanager to detect and respond to issues in real-time.<br />
        <strong>Optimized Performance</strong>: Helps identify resource bottlenecks and optimize cluster workloads.<br />
    </Text2>

    <Text3>
        <strong>Seamless Integration</strong>: Natively supports Prometheus, making deployment straightforward.<br />
        <strong>Custom Metrics</strong>: Allows administrators to define and export specific Proxmox VE metrics.<br />
        <strong>Scalability</strong>: Suitable for both small clusters and large-scale Proxmox deployments.<br />
    </Text3>
</Overview3Cols>
